# Terraform Azure Network and Virtual Machine Configuration

This Terraform configuration sets up an Azure Virtual Network, Subnet, Public IP, Network Interface, Storage Account, and Virtual Machine. The configuration uses input variables to allow customization of the resources.

## Prerequisites

- [Terraform](https://www.terraform.io/downloads.html) installed
- An Azure account with appropriate permissions
- Azure CLI installed and authenticated (`az login`)

## Files

- `main.tf`: The main Terraform configuration file
